                  <summary>Abbreviated Antiphonary for the Whole Year, ድጓ፡ (Mäzmur Chants and Hymns for Feast Days), with musical notation, owned by Nəburä ‘Ǝdə Dəmeṭəros Gäbrä Maryam</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="185r" facs="005"/><title>Chants called Mäzǝmur, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ: መዝሙር:</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ናሁ፡ ወጠንኩ፡ ጺሒፈ፡ መዝሙር፡ እምዓመት፡ እስከ፡ ዓመት፡ ምል፡ በ፩ ብፁዕ፡ አንተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወተሐውር፡ ቅድመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጸሊ፡ በእንቲአነ፡ ውስተ፡ ርእሰ፡ ዓውደ፡ ዓመት፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ ተዝካርከ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ዘሀለወከ፡ ታእምር፡</incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>
                  <note>with musical notation. Abbreviated Antiphonary for the Whole Year, Dǝggwa, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድጓ፡</foreign></note>
